I heard Wu talking about it.

00:05:29.459 --> 00:05:30.819
Everyone said so.

00:05:31.379 --> 00:05:32.540
There's no smoke without fire.

00:05:33.499 --> 00:05:35.300
Why should I
waste my effort applying then?

00:05:35.300 --> 00:05:36.019
Am I right?

00:05:36.019 --> 00:05:37.540
You don't even know where the smoke is.

00:05:37.540 --> 00:05:38.890
Yet you say that you see the fire.

00:05:39.060 --> 00:05:39.820
If that's the case,

00:05:39.830 --> 00:05:42.100
Jiao won't make it to Tsinghua
or Peking University then.

00:05:42.100 --> 00:05:43.420
She might as well not study.

00:05:44.100 --> 00:05:45.420
You're shifting the concept.

00:05:45.420 --> 00:05:46.459
It's a different matter.

