00:06:23.300 --> 00:06:24.379
Calm down.

00:06:24.379 --> 00:06:25.740
Be careful with the baby.

00:06:26.210 --> 00:06:28.459
Even though your husband
is not related to you by blood,

00:06:28.699 --> 00:06:31.139
