saved that drowning kid

00:09:17.099 --> 00:09:18.579
and gotten himself killed.

00:09:20.660 --> 00:09:22.699
It's all Shen Mingzhu's fault.

00:09:24.020 --> 00:09:26.459
She's a cancer.

00:09:27.579 --> 00:09:30.140
No wonder
her biological parents abandoned her.

00:09:30.380 --> 00:09:31.619
Enough.

