00:10:15.099 --> 00:10:17.300
That's why I drove Jianqi's car back.

00:10:17.900 --> 00:10:19.420
It's all Shen Mingzhu's fault.

00:10:19.540 --> 00:10:21.099
The Shen family is to blame.

00:10:21.099 --> 00:10:22.099
They're all monsters.

00:10:22.099 --> 00:10:24.420
