00:12:19.099 --> 00:12:20.260
No, we don't want it anymore.

00:12:21.219 --> 00:12:22.619
Where are you going, Mom?

00:12:22.960 --> 00:12:24.950
Xiaoni is crying. I'm going
to see what's happening.

00:12:25.140 --> 00:12:27.339
Xiaoni is my half sister.

00:12:27.339 --> 00:12:29.459
She's not related to you by blood.

00:12:29.619 --> 00:12:30.300
Listen.

00:12:30.300 --> 00:12:32.750
The neighbours just had dinner
and have nothing to do now.

00:12:32.760 --> 00:12:34.060
Feel free to cry or laugh outside,

00:12:34.070 --> 00:12:35.540
or it's okay
if you don't want to do both,

00:12:35.540 --> 00:12:36.750
they're eager to watch your drama.

00:12:38.900 --> 00:12:40.660
I'm not scared.

00:12:41.660 --> 00:12:43.060
I'm not the one who's cheating.

00:12:50.900 --> 00:12:52.859
The downside of
living in an old building.

00:12:52.939 --> 00:12:55.219
