every household's business.

00:12:55.220 --> 00:12:56.870
I told you to move,
you're the one who said no.

00:12:56.880 --> 00:12:57.910
Where should we move then?

00:12:58.740 --> 00:12:59.699
No matter where we move,

00:12:59.699 --> 00:13:02.300
Ni Debao should face the music.

00:13:04.099 --> 00:13:04.939
Scum.

00:13:06.739 --> 00:13:07.939
You don't deserve the incense.

00:13:19.540 --> 00:13:20.500
What are you doing?

00:13:21.170 --> 00:13:22.650
The diamonds are scattered everywhere.

00:13:23.859 --> 00:13:24.660
Stop it.

00:13:24.660 --> 00:13:26.979
It's not that valuable anyway.

00:13:27.440 --> 00:13:28.260
You don't understand.

